                    "name": "Mind-Numbing Touch",
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "When a soul eater hits a creature with its claw Strike, the creature must succeed at a DC 23 Fortitude save or become <a aonid=\"37\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">stupefied 1</a> (stupefied 2 on a critical failure). Further damage dealt by the soul eater increases the stupefied value by 1 on a failed save, to a maximum of stupefied 4. This condition value decreases by 1 each time the creature gets a full night's rest. As long as the creature is stupefied by a soul eater, rest does not decrease any <a aonid=\"9\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">doomed</a> value that creature might have.",
